OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1782155909
OL,3,CE-bike rider dead after crash with
OL,4,Cmoped
OL,6,FAn e-bike rider has died after a crash
OL,7,Fwith a moped in Bradford.
OL,9,FThe 22-year-old was riding on Great
OL,10,FHorton Road when he was involved in a
OL,11,Fcollision at 2.17pm on Friday, 19 June.
OL,13,FHe died in hospital on Saturday.
OL,15,FTwo men, aged 22 and 27, who were
OL,16,Farrested on suspicion of causing
OL,17,Fserious injury by dangerous driving,
OL,18,Fhave been bailed pending further
OL,19,Fenquiries.
